##ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project analyzes loan application data to uncover the key factors influencing loan approval and rejection decisions.
Using interactive dashboards and data visualization techniques, it delivers actionable insights into applicant behavior, financial profiles, and approval trends to support realistic and data-driven decision-making.
The project was developed as part of my data analysis learning journey, showcasing my ability to transform raw data into meaningful business insights using Power BI and Excel.
## Project Objectives
Analyze approved vs rejected loan applications
Identify factors influencing loan approval:
Annual Income
Credit Score
Loan Amount
Employment Length
Visualize trends using interactive dashboards
Support realistic loan approval decisions through insights
